<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/committee-on-climate-change> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Committee on Climate Change (CCC) advises the government on emissions targets and reports to Parliament on progress made in reducing greenhouse gas emissions. CCC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero ."@en .
